examples.en: He turned abruptly and walked away.
The road ends abruptly in a drop to the sea.
He told them abruptly and without ceremony that they would have to leave.
My woolgathering was abruptly interrupted by a question from the flight attendant.
I gave a sudden shout of surprise when the shower abruptly turned ice-cold.
...the crash abruptly wakened the dozers on the bus...
...was abruptly cashiered after money was found missing from the safe...
